\begin_layout Section
Presentation of the subject
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The subject asks to elaborate a human-machine interface in the form of a
 website.
 This website’s aim is to allow the users to barter their goods.
 The interface was designed with the following constraints:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
To respect the standards required by the web
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
To allow an immediate handling
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
To give information where necessary
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
To make interactions intuitive
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
